{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/til/technical-writing/one/08-paragraphs/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bestalign's dev blog","categories":[{"displayText":"홈","priority":0,"name":"home","url":"/"},{"displayText":"TIL","priority":1,"name":"til","url":"/til"},{"displayText":"개발","priority":2,"name":"dev","url":"/dev"},{"displayText":"독서","priority":3,"name":"reading","url":"/reading"},{"displayText":"번역","priority":4,"name":"translation","url":"/translation"},{"displayText":"일기","priority":5,"name":"everydaylife","url":"/everydaylife"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"272069c8-b4d1-5ad2-a06f-3d80d4cb0538","excerpt":"The work of writing is simply this: untangling the dependencies among the parts of a topic, and presenting those parts in a logical stream that enables the…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>The work of writing is simply this: untangling the dependencies among the parts of a topic, and presenting those parts in a logical stream that enables the reader to understand you.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>글쓰기는 간단히 말해 다음과 같다: 주제 안에 복잡하에 얽혀있는 내용을 논리적으로 풀어써서 독자가 이해할 수 있게 하는 것.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"적절한-첫-문장을-써라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%A0%88%ED%95%9C-%EC%B2%AB-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%A5%EC%9D%84-%EC%8D%A8%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"적절한 첫 문장을 써라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적절한 첫 문장을 써라</h4>\n<p>문단의 첫 문장은 가장 중요하다. 첫 문장은 그 문단의 핵심내용을 가지고 있어야 한다. 바쁜 독자들은 첫 문장만 읽고 문단을 건너뛰기도 하므로 첫 문장을 가장 신경써서 써야한다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#example\" aria-label=\"example permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example</h5>\n<p>A loop runs the same block of code multiple times. For example, suppose you wrote a block of code that detected whether an input line ended with a period. To evaluate a million input lines, create a loop that runs a million times.</p>\n<h4 id=\"각-문단마다-하나의-주제에-집중하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%81-%EB%AC%B8%EB%8B%A8%EB%A7%88%EB%8B%A4-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%A3%BC%EC%A0%9C%EC%97%90-%EC%A7%91%EC%A4%91%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"각 문단마다 하나의 주제에 집중하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>각 문단마다 하나의 주제에 집중하라</h4>\n<p>각 문단은 하나의 주제에 대해서만 이야기해야한다. 이전 혹은 다음 문단의 내용이 있다면 삭제하거나 적절한 문단으로 옮겨라.</p>\n<h4 id=\"문단은-너무-짧거나-길면-안된다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EB%8B%A8%EC%9D%80-%EB%84%88%EB%AC%B4-%EC%A7%A7%EA%B1%B0%EB%82%98-%EA%B8%B8%EB%A9%B4-%EC%95%88%EB%90%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"문단은 너무 짧거나 길면 안된다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문단은 너무 짧거나 길면 안된다</h4>\n<p>너무 긴 문단은 독자들이 겁먹게 만든다. 보통 한 문단에 3-5 문장 정도가 적당하고 7 문장이 넘어갈 경우 문단을 나누는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<p>반대로 한 문장으로만 이루어진 문단이 많다면 구성에 문제가 있는 것이다. 만약 그렇다면 문단을 합치거나 리스트로 만드는 것을 고려해라.</p>\n<h4 id=\"왜-무엇을-어떻게\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%99%9C-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%84-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C\" aria-label=\"왜 무엇을 어떻게 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>왜, 무엇을, 어떻게</h4>\n<p>좋은 문단은 다음의 질문에 대답해야 한다:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>독자에게 <strong>무엇을</strong> 말하고 싶은가?</li>\n<li><strong>왜</strong> 이것이 독자에게 중요한가?</li>\n<li>독자는 이 지식을 <strong>어떻게</strong> 사용해야 하는가? 혹은, 독자는 이 내용을 진실인지 <strong>어떻게</strong> 알아야 하는가?</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"example-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#example-1\" aria-label=\"example 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example</h5>\n<p>&#x3C;무엇을>The garp() function returns the delta between a dataset’s mean and median.&#x3C;/무엇을>&#x3C;왜>Many people believe unquestioningly that a mean always holds the truth. However, a mean is easily influenced by a few very large or very small data points.&#x3C;/왜>&#x3C;어떻게>Call garp() to help determine whether a few very large or very small data points are influencing the mean too much. A relatively small garp() value suggests that the mean is more meaningful than when the garp() value is relatively high.&#x3C;/어떻게></p>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/tech-writing/one/paragraphs\">Google Dev Technical Writing 1 - Paragraphs</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Paragraphs","category":"til","date":"July 05, 2021","updated":null,"description":null,"tags":["technical writing"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/07-lists-and-tables-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Lists and Tables 2"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/shell/direnv/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"direnv - 폴더별 환경관리"}}},"pageContex